om/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/sampha-steve-lacy-bad-habit-cover-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/sampha-steve-lacy-bad-habit-cover-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/sampha-steve-lacy-bad-habit-cover-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sampha">Sampha</a>在 BBC 广播 1 台的“Live Lounge Month”节目中重新演绎了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/steve-lacy">Steve Lacy</a>的“Bad Habit”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/steve-lacy-live-at-reading-review-setlist-photos-3489850">史蒂夫·莱西在雷丁节：吉他大师进入他的帝国阶段</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位创作型歌手上周选择了这首 2022 年热门歌曲作为他在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodrigo-doja-cat-royal-blood-and-more-lead-line-up-for-bbc-radio-1-live-lounge-month-3493501">Live Lounge Mouth</a>演出的封面，期间他在嘶嘶作响、简洁的鼓声中唱歌并弹奏钢琴。</p><p>他还演奏了上周发行的新专辑《Lahai》中自己的歌曲《Only》。</p><p>看看下面的表演。 </p><p><iframe title="Sampha - 现场休息室的坏习惯" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/KXkIv_s_uLE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe title="Sampha - 仅限现场休息室" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/jlgsVWGUS60?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Sampha 翻唱的《Bad Habit》是 BBC Radio 1 Live Lounge 月推出的众多翻唱之一，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/usher">亚瑟小子</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-usher-cover-daniel-caesar-and-hers-best-part-on-bbc-radio-1-live-lounge-3520222">翻唱了 Daniel Caesar 和 HER 的《Best Part》</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/troye-sivan">Troye Sivan</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-troye-sivan-cover-billie-eilishs-what-was-i-made-for-in-bbc-radio-1s-live-lounge-3508521">翻唱了 Billie Eilish 的《What Was I Made For》</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/doja-cat">Doja Cat</a>是今年 10 月为期一个月的节目的最后一位嘉宾，她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-doja-cat-cover-hiatus-kaiyotes-red-room-on-bbc-radio-1-live-lounge-3523572">翻唱了 Hiatus Kaiyote 的“Red Room</a> ”。</p><p>在 Sampha 的新专辑发行之前，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sampha-wants-to-interrogate-spirituality-on-new-album-lahai-3513822">在 LP 上公开了他想如何“质疑灵性”</a> 。</p><p>他在 2019 年“发生了很多事情”之前就开始制作这张专辑，并在 2020 年迎来了他的第一个女儿。“我成为了一名父亲，”他在最近的问答中解释道。 “我只是想知道生活和重大问题，感觉需要抓住一些东西或描绘我的生活鸟瞰图，因为我觉得每一天都在进入每一天。”</p><p>桑帕说，在《Lahai》中，他想“审问灵性”，并在制作专辑时“质疑”一切。</p><p> “成为一名父亲是一件非常关乎生存的事，”他说。 “我觉得，对我来说，音乐只是一个我可以去了解自己对某些事情的感受的地方。这对我来说是一种治疗。”</p><p> 7 月，Sampha 发行了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sampha-releases-spirit-2-0-visualiser-fist-single-in-six-years-album-process-3463495-3463495">六年来的首张单曲“Spirit 2.0”，</a>令歌迷们大吃一惊。这是他自 2017 年获得水星奖的首张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/sampha-process-album-review-1964828">《Process》</a>以来的首张专辑。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-samphas-cover-of-steve-lacys-bad-habit-3524192">聆听 Sampha 翻唱 Steve Lacy 的《Bad Habit》的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
尚格·云顿 (Jean-Claude Van Damme) 因在《老友记》中的亮相而感到尴尬https://www.nme.com/news/tv/jean-claude-van-damme-is-embarrassed-by-his-friends-appearance-3524175?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=jean-claude-van-damme-因朋友的外表而感到尴尬Max PilleyFri, 27 Oct 2023 20:45:04 +0000 NewsTV News https://www.nme.com/?p=3524175 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/jean_claude_van_damme.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="尚格·云顿" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/jean_claude_van_damme.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/jean_claude_van_damme-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/jean_claude_van_damme-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/jean_claude_van_damme-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/jean_claude_van_damme-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/jean_claude_van_damme-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我的演技太差了。我看起来太像火腿了……我为自己感到羞耻。”</p><p>尚格·云顿<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/jean-claude-van-damme-is-embarrassed-by-his-friends-appearance-3524175">(Jean-Claude Van Damme) 因在《老友记》中露面而感到尴尬的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/jean_claude_van_damme.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="尚格·云顿" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/jean_claude_van_damme.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/jean_claude_van_damme-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/jean_claude_van_damme-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/jean_claude_van_damme-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/jean_claude_van_damme-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/jean_claude_van_damme-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jean-claude-van-damme">尚格·云顿 (Jean-Claude Van Damme)</a>一直在谈论他 1996 年在<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/friends"><i>《老友记》</i></a>中出演一集时所经历的尴尬。</p><p>这位比利时动作明星在情景喜剧“超级碗之后的人：第二部分”第二季中扮演了自己。情节中，云顿在纽约拍摄电影时，瑞秋（<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jennifer-aniston">詹妮弗·安妮斯顿饰</a>）和莫妮卡（柯特妮·考克斯饰）争夺云顿的芳心。</p><p>不过，这位演员在接受<a href="https://nypost.com/2023/10/25/entertainment/jean-claude-van-damme-ashamed-of-friends-episode-with-jen-aniston-courteney-cox/"><i>《纽约邮报》</i></a>采访时透露，回顾这一集他感到很尴尬。</p><p> “我的演技太差了。我看起来太像火腿了……我为自己感到羞耻，”他说。 “那些女孩，她们走过去亲吻我，亲吻我的嘴唇。我不知道该做什么、怎么做……这很奇怪。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="老友记：莫妮卡和瑞秋因尚格云顿而争吵（第 2 季剪辑）| TBS" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/TUVXVM4CJIM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>云顿承认，在出演该剧之前，他对这部剧并不是很熟悉，但他对自己受到的待遇表示赞赏，称其为“一段美好的回忆”和“令人惊叹”。</p><p> “我对这个节目了解不多。所以当我去看演出时，我看到那两个漂亮的女孩，她们说这是现在世界上最热门的演出。所以我很高兴。他们非常友善。”</p><p>在<i>《老友记》</i>的其他新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-ed-sheeran-serenade-courtney-cox-with-friends-inspired-song-3502327">艾德·希兰最近为柯特妮·考克斯演唱了他的新歌《美国小镇》的一小段小夜曲</a>，他解释说这首歌曲的灵感来自于该剧。 “<i>我们在小白盒子里吃中国菜/过我们在《老友记》中看到的生活</i>，”希兰在歌曲前副歌部分唱道。这首歌收录在他九月发行的新专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/ed-sheeran-autumn-variations-review-lyrics-tracklist-3505933">秋季变奏曲</a>》中。</p><p>八月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/friends-writer-claims-cast-were-aggressive-and-dire-to-work-with-3487890"><i>《老友记》的</i>编剧林佩蒂声称该剧的演员们“很有攻击性”，而且合作起来“很糟糕”</a> 。林在她的回忆录中写道，她在该剧第七季中写道：“演员们似乎不高兴被束缚在一部陈旧的老剧中，而他们可以拓展自己的业务，我觉得他们不断地想知道每个给定的剧本如何会专门为他们服务。”</p><p>云顿与 2023 年格斗游戏<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/mortal-kombat-1"><i>《真人快打 1》</i></a>中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/mortal-kombat-1-shows-off-bloodsport-era-jean-claude-van-damme-cameo-3495154">角色约翰尼·凯奇的肖像和声音相似</a>。</p><p>尚格·云顿<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/jean-claude-van-damme-is-embarrassed-by-his-friends-appearance-3524175">(Jean-Claude Van Damme) 因在《老友记》中露面而感到尴尬的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
前 QOTSA 贝斯手 Nick Oliveri 宣布推出两首合辑并分享与 Slash 合作的《Chains And Shackles》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/former-qotsa-bassist-nick-oliveri-announces-two-compilations-and-shares-chains-and-shackles-featuring-slash-3524166?utm_source=rss&utm_medium= rss&utm_campaign=前 qotsa-bassist-nick-oliveri-announces-two-compilations-and-shares-chains-and-shackles-featuring-slashAnagricel Duran Fri, 27 Oct 2023 20:15:24 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3524166 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Nick-Oliveri-and-Slash.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="尼克·奥利维里和斯莱什。图片来源：大卫·沃尔夫 - 帕特里克和哈里·杜兰特，来自 GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Nick-Oliveri-and-Slash.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Nick-Oliveri-and-Slash-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Nick-Oliveri-and-Slash-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Nick-Oliveri-and-Slash-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Nick-Oliveri-and-Slash-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Nick-Oliveri-and-Slash-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这首歌是这位标志性吉他手 2010 年同名 LP 中的片段</p><p>前<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/former-qotsa-bassist-nick-oliveri-announces-two-compilations-and-shares-chains-and-shackles-featuring-slash-3524166">QOTSA 贝斯手 Nick Oliveri 宣布推出两首合辑，并分享与 Slash 合作的《Chains And Shackles》，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Nick-Oliveri-and-Slash.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="尼克·奥利维里和斯莱什。图片来源：大卫·沃尔夫 - 帕特里克和哈里·杜兰特，来自 GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Nick-Oliveri-and-Slash.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Nick-Oliveri-and-Slash-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Nick-Oliveri-and-Slash-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Nick-Oliveri-and-Slash-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Nick-Oliveri-and-Slash-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Nick-Oliveri-and-Slash-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/queens-of-the-stone-age">Queens Of The Stone Age</a>的前贝斯手 Nick Oliveri 宣布了两张新合辑，并分享了与<a href="/artists/slash">Slash</a>合作的歌曲“Chains And Shackles”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/queens-of-the-stone-age-josh-homme-in-times-new-roman-tour-3454749">《石器时代的女王》：“这张专辑听起来就像活着的感觉一样残酷”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这两首合辑收录了奥利维里整个职业生涯的曲目。两张专辑分别名为“NO Hits At All Vols.8”和“NO Hits At All Vols.9”，均定于 1 月 19 日通过 Heavy Psych Sounds 发行。<a href="https://www.heavypsychsounds.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>预订专辑。</p><p>这位音乐家分享了《NO Hits At All Vols.8》的开场曲《Chains and Shackles》，这标志着 2010 年与 Slash 合作的首首正式歌曲。</p><p>这首歌是这位标志性吉他手 2010 年同名 LP 中的一个片段，并将通过奥利维尔的合辑正式发行。 《Chains and Shackles》由 Eric Valentine 制作，他曾制作过 Queens Of The Stone Age 2002 年专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-queens-of-the-stone-age-6631-317548">Songs For The Deaf</a> 》。</p><p>奥利维里即将推出的两张合辑都包含未发行的材料，涵盖了这位音乐家多年来参与的各个乐队和独奏项目。其中一些乐队和项目包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mondo-generator">Mondo Generator</a> 、他的 Death Acoustic 项目、Dead End America 等。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="NICK OLIVERI (feat. Slash) - Chains And Shackles // HEAVY PSYCH SOUNDS Records" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/WrsFkOD1Qtw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <strong>&#39;根本没有点击量。 8&#39; 曲目列表是：<br /></strong><br /> <strong>1.《锁链与枷锁》（Slash，尼克·奥利维里）</strong><br /> <strong>2.“真相比小说更奇怪”（尼克·奥利维里的《死亡原声》）</strong><br /> <strong>3.“我没有死”（无法用雷克斯的一切命名的人）</strong><br /> <strong>4.《Back Off Boogaloo》（尼克·奥利维里和药店牛仔）</strong><br /> <strong>5.“领主们驾临”（死亡机器3）</strong><br /> <strong>6.“她想离开”（尼克·奥利维里的死亡原声）</strong><br /> <strong>7.“Outlaw Scumfuc”（尼克·奥利维里的《Death Acoustic》）</strong> </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/Cy0472sLzpf/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546